<SECOND>AM-Summit-First Ladies, 1st Ld-Writethru, a0792,1,000</SECOND>
<HEAD>Nancy and Raisa Reunited; Things Go Mostly Well</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: To CORRECT name of cathedral to Assumption sted Annunciation,
SUB 12th graf, ``The Soviet...''
^By SUSANNE M. SCHAFER</NOTE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>MOSCOW (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
