<FIRST>r i AM-Vietnam-Cambodia     05-29 0366</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Vietnam-Cambodia,0379</SECOND>
<HEAD>Khmer Rouge Denounce Vietnamese Withdrawal from Cambodia</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BANGKOK, Thailand (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
