<FIRST>r p AM-Summit-Dukakis 1stLd-Writethru a0774 05-29 0290</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Summit-Dukakis, 1st Ld-Writethru, a0774,270</SECOND>
<NOTE>EDs: SUBS 4th graf to CORRECT call letters to BBC.</NOTE>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
