CATION>'s biggest city. <PERSON> Zia </PERSON> said that he had repeatedly reminded <PERSON> Junejo </PERSON> to improve the law and order situation and to speed up the process of Islamization. But he said <PERSON> Junejo </PERSON> took the view that he had to go along with the wishes of the Assembly, which favored a gradual move to Islamism.
