<PERSON> R.P </PERSON>. <PERSON> Cochran </PERSON> and <PERSON> William </PERSON> <PERSON> Steves </PERSON> <PERSON> Ring </PERSON>, who has performed more than 100 heart transplants since 1984. <PERSON> Jones </PERSON>' operation in April was the first infant heart transplant in <LOCATION> Dallas </LOCATION>. There have been 37 infant heart transplants in the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION>, including <PERSON> Jones </PERSON>' second operation. Twenty-one babies are still living, including <PERSON> Baby </PERSON> <PERSON> Moses </PERSON>, who received the first transplant at <LOCATION> Loma </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Linda </LOCATION>.
